snippet.textDisplay: Dear Coke Studio, Please for the love of God. Stop. This is the worst you can do to a classic like Anokha Laadla. You have already ruined great voices like Saieen Zahoor, Misha Shafi, Jaaved Bashir. Stop now this obsession of bringing in experimenting music directors for each song. Stop this obsession with Momina. Stop this over-instrumentation of everything. This song could have been done so much better by Rizwan and Muazzam or Ataullah sahab. Just stop. And for heaven's sake atleast put the correct subtitles....I don't even know what to make of this. The singer singing "mann bole rakh loon main man mein" while the subtitles say "mann bole rakh loon nainan mein"....You don't necessarily have to bring in a couplet from 5 different songs to make it one and have us pretend that its working. Much disappointed with this season as a whole.
snippet.textOriginal: Dear Coke Studio, Please for the love of God. Stop. This is the worst you can do to a classic like Anokha Laadla. You have already ruined great voices like Saieen Zahoor, Misha Shafi, Jaaved Bashir. Stop now this obsession of bringing in experimenting music directors for each song. Stop this obsession with Momina. Stop this over-instrumentation of everything. This song could have been done so much better by Rizwan and Muazzam or Ataullah sahab. Just stop. And for heaven's sake atleast put the correct subtitles....I don't even know what to make of this. The singer singing "mann bole rakh loon main man mein" while the subtitles say "mann bole rakh loon nainan mein"....You don't necessarily have to bring in a couplet from 5 different songs to make it one and have us pretend that its working. Much disappointed with this season as a whole.
